CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777817461
OL,3,CSwindon barbershop owner fined #2,200
OL,4,Cfor illegally dumping bags of rubbish
OL,6,FA barbershop owner from Swindon has
OL,7,Fbeen fined more than #2,200 after
OL,8,Fwaste belonging to him was found
OL,9,Fdumped in the Oxfordshire countryside.
OL,11,FAndre Niehues, 40, paid an unknown man
OL,12,F#20 to remove rubbish from overflowing
OL,13,Fbins near to his shop last year.
OL,15,FBut, rather than properly dispose of
OL,16,Fthe waste - which included plastic
OL,17,Fbags of rubbish and cardboard boxes -
OL,18,Fthe man ditched it near the village of
OL,19,FBuscot, in Oxfordshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
