FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777817461
OL,3,CSwindon barbershop owner fined #2,200
OL,4,Cfor illegally dumping bags of rubbish
OL,6,FAn environmental enforcement officer
OL,7,Ffrom the Vale of White Horse District
OL,8,FCouncil, who attended the site,
OL,9,Frecovered evidence linking the dumped
OL,10,Fwaste to Niehues' address.
OL,12,FNiehues, when interviewed, admitted
OL,13,Fthat he did not check whether the man
OL,14,Fwas a registered waste carrier.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
