OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777817461
OL,3,CSwindon barbershop owner fined #2,200
OL,4,Cfor illegally dumping bags of rubbish
OL,6,FHe also failed to record full contact
OL,7,Fdetails or receive any paperwork, such
OL,8,Fas a waste transfer note.
OL,10,FThe only detail he was able to provide
OL,11,Fwas a first name and a phone number,
OL,12,Fwhich was found to be disconnected.
OL,14,FDespite attempts to trace the other
OL,15,Fperson involved, the council was
OL,16,Funable to identify them.
OL,18,FNiehues was prosecuted by the Vale of
OL,19,FWhite Horse District Council and,
OL,20,Feventually, pled guilty to four duty
OL,21,Fof care offences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
