OL,3,CSwindon barbershop owner fined #2,200
OL,4,Cfor illegally dumping bags of rubbish
OL,6,FHe was sentenced on Friday, April 24
OL,7,Fand ordered to pay fines totalling up
OL,8,Fto #2,235.10.
